  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "This is a fork of [awesome link](https://github.com/akullpp/awesome-java) with new structure, additional license info and github's star info for every link, with a lot of new links (all non-mobile github projects with 390 or more star) and so on. **The russian version is [in this place](https://github.com/Vedenin/useful-java-links/tree/master/link-rus)**.  \n**The \"Hello Worlds examples\" project is [in this place](https://github.com/Vedenin/useful-java-links/tree/master/helloworlds)**.",
